This is Perl module AnyEvent::Twitter::Plugin::Yammer.

INSTALLATION

AnyEvent::Twitter::Plugin::Yammer installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

% cpan AnyEvent::Twitter::Plugin::Yammer

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

% perl Makefile.PL
% make && make test

Then install it:

% make install

DOCUMENTATION

AnyEvent::Twitter::Plugin::Yammer documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

% perldoc AnyEvent::Twitter::Plugin::Yammer
